00:34:35,891 --> 00:34:38,041
♪ <i>Fading into ruin</i> ♪

736
00:34:38,109 --> 00:34:40,860
♪ <i>Nowhere left to go</i> ♪

737
00:34:40,929 --> 00:34:43,647
♪ <i>Hanging on a feeling</i> ♪

738
00:34:43,698 --> 00:34:46,699
♪ <i>Losing all control</i> ♪

739
00:34:46,768 --> 00:34:49,469
♪ <i>Cannot find the healing</i> ♪

