00:34:49,538 --> 00:34:51,387
♪ <i>Done it all before</i> ♪

741
00:34:51,457 --> 00:34:54,307
Avoid injury to
the splenic vein.

742
00:34:56,295 --> 00:34:58,294
♪ <i>I can't help</i> ♪

743
00:34:58,363 --> 00:35:01,031
You see that? That
pulsing little worm?

